<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ لَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اعْلَمْ أَنَّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا»</span> تَنْصِبُ النَّكِرَاتِ بِغَيْرِ تَنْوِينٍ: إِذَا بَاشَرَتِ النَّكِرَةَ، وَلَمْ تَتَكَرَّرْ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">نَحْوُ:</span> لَا رَجُلَ فِي الدَّارِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَإِنْ لَمْ تُبَاشِرْهَا:</span> وَجَبَ الرَّفْعُ وَوَجَبَ تَكْرَارُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">نَحْوُ:</span> لَا فِي الدَّارِ رَجُلٌ وَلَا امْرَأَةٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِنْ تَكَرَّرَتْ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا»</span>: جَازَ إِعْمَالُهَا وَإِلْغَاؤُهَا -<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنْ شِئْتَ قُلْتَ:</span> لَا رَجُلَ فِي الدَّارِ وَلَا امْرَأَةَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ شِئْتَ قُلْتَ:</span> لَا رَجُلٌ فِي الدَّارِ وَلَا امْرَأَةٌ ـ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>